        "message": "Revert \"LU-9043 test: remove conf-sanity test 24a ALWAYS_EXCEPT\"\n\nThis reverts commit 101ee4909eeb23c66ae2dbb0690e3b47db207951.\n\nconf-sanity tests 32a and 32d are failing for ZFS testing. Reverting this patch to see if test 24a has an impact on tests that are run after it.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=conf-sanity clientdistro=el7 serverdistro=el7 osscount=1 ostcount=2 mdscount=1 mdtcount=1 clientcount=2 ostfilesystemtype=zfs mdtfilesystemtype=zfs\n\nChange-Id: I7326afaee1f344cb614869fd5dbad3e04d01310c\nSigned-off-by:James Nunez <james.a.nunez@intel.com>\n"
